---
const SITE_NAME = "The-Circle";
const DISCORD_INVITE = "https://discord.gg/9rPcHQZ7SH";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Discord • {SITE_NAME}</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="The-Circle Discord: a clean, low-pressure server for hanging out, voice, games, music, and movie nights."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <header class="top">
        <div class="container nav">
          <a class="brand" href="/">
            <span class="mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span>{SITE_NAME}</span>
          </a>

          <nav class="links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/league">League</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a class="pill" href="/join">Join</a>
          </nav>

          <a class="pill mobileJoin" href="/join">Join</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="container">
        <section class="hero">
          <div class="welcome">
            <h1>The-Circle Discord</h1>
            <p class="lead">
              The purpose is simple: a reliable Discord you can drop into when you want people around.
              Hang out, play something, watch a movie, listen to music, or just chill in voice — no pressure to be “active.”
            </p>

            <div class="cta">
              <a class="btn primary" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
              <a class="btn ghost" href="#features">See what’s different</a>
              <a class="btn ghost" href="#how">How it works</a>
            </div>

            <p class="fine">
              Lurking is fine. You don’t have to introduce yourself like it’s a job interview.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card" id="features">
          <h2>What makes it better than the average “friends server”</h2>
          <p class="note">
            Most servers are either huge + chaotic, or small + messy. This one is built to be clean, useful, and actually used.
          </p>

          <div class="grid">
            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Drop-in voice</h3>
              <p>Hop in to talk, idle, or just hang out while you’re doing your own thing.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Movies / streams</h3>
              <p>Watch together like a living room. Come and go whenever.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Casual game nights</h3>
              <p>Find people to play with without the sweaty clan vibe.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Boosted quality</h3>
              <p>Higher voice quality + better streaming options thanks to server boosts.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Private voice channels (on demand)</h3>
              <p>Spin up a private VC for your group when you want privacy — without killing the public vibe.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Actually moderated</h3>
              <p>MEE6 Pro + clean permissions + organized channels so it doesn’t turn into a cluttered junk drawer.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>The vibe</h2>

          <div class="pills">
            <span class="pill2">Drop-in energy</span>
            <span class="pill2">Low pressure</span>
            <span class="pill2">Organized channels</span>
            <span class="pill2">Voice/stream boosted quality</span>
            <span class="pill2">Private & clean</span>
            <span class="pill2">Come & go</span>
            <span class="pill2">Adult-friendly</span>
            <span class="pill2">No drama</span>
          </div>

          <p class="note">
            The goal isn’t to build a “community” that feels like homework. It’s to have a place that’s there when you need it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card" id="how">
          <h2>How it works</h2>

          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="num">1</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Join and lurk if you want</h3>
                <p>No forced intros. No weird onboarding. Take your time.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <div class="num">2</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Jump into voice when you feel like it</h3>
                <p>Some people talk, some people just hang out. Both are normal here.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <div class="num">3</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Use it for what you need</h3>
                <p>Games, movies, music, or just background company — whatever.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <div class="num">4</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Want privacy? Make a private VC</h3>
                <p>Keep your group conversation private without leaving the server.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cta">
            <a class="btn primary" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/discord/rules">Discord rules</a>
          </div>

          <p class="fine">
            If you want to add more “custom features” here later, this page is set up to scale without becoming a wall of text.
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container foot">
          <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE_NAME}</span>
          <span class="muted">Discord</span>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <style is:global>
      html, body { height: 100%; }

      body{
        margin:0;
        min-height:100vh;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);

        background-image:
          radial-gradient(900px 500px at 15% 10%, rgba(9,255,3,0.14), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(800px 450px at 85% 15%, rgba(120,170,255,0.18), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(700px 450px at 55% 95%, rgba(255,170,120,0.10), transparent 55%),
          linear-gradient(#070a0f, #070a0f);

        background-repeat:no-repeat;
        background-size:100% 100%;
        background-attachment:fixed;
      }

      a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
      .container{ max-width: 1020px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 18px; }

      .page{ min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
      main{ flex:1; }

      /* Top nav */
      .top{
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        background: rgba(7,10,15,0.55);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      }

      .nav{
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:space-between;
        padding:14px 18px;
        gap:14px;
      }

      .brand{
        display:flex;
        gap:10px;
        align-items:center;
        font-weight:800;
        letter-spacing:-0.02em;
        white-space:nowrap;
      }

      .mark{
        width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:999px;background:#09ff03;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(9,255,3,0.12), 0 0 28px rgba(9,255,3,0.25);
      }

      .links{ display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:center; }
      .links a{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); font-size:14px; }
      .links a:hover{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); }

      .pill{
        padding:10px 12px;border-radius:999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(9,255,3,0.24);
        background: rgba(9,255,3,0.10);
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      }
      .mobileJoin{ display:none; }

      /* Hero welcome */
      .hero{ padding: 34px 0 10px; }

      .welcome{
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
        padding: 22px;
      }

      h1{ margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 40px; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
      h2{ margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
      h3{ margin:0 0 6px; font-size: 16px; }

      .lead{
        margin:0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.74);
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 92ch;
      }

      .note{
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.70);
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 92ch;
      }

      .fine{
        margin-top: 12px;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .cta{
        display:flex;
        gap:12px;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .btn{
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:center;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
        transition: transform .14s ease, background .14s ease;
      }
      .btn:hover{ transform: translateY(-1px); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }
      .btn.primary{ border-color: rgba(9,255,3,0.22); background: rgba(9,255,3,0.10); }
      .btn.ghost{ background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }

      /* Cards */
      .card{
        margin: 18px 0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      }

      .grid{
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr));
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .tile{
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      .tile p{
        margin:0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .pills{
        display:flex;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }

      .pill2{
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .steps{
        display:grid;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }

      .step{
        display:flex;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items:flex-start;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      .num{
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:center;
        font-weight: 900;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
        border: 1px solid rgba(9,255,3,0.20);
        background: rgba(9,255,3,0.08);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(9,255,3,0.06) inset;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }

      /* Footer */
      .footer{
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
        background: rgba(7,10,15,0.35);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .foot{
        display:flex;
        justify-content:space-between;
        gap:12px;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
      }

      .muted{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }

      @media (max-width: 980px){
        .grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }

      @media (max-width: 820px){
        .links{ display:none; }
        .mobileJoin{ display:inline-flex; }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
